thread.title: Kevin O Brien
thread.title_full: Hunt Office reviewed by Kevin O Brien

author: Kevin O Brien
title: Kevin O Brien
text: I have issues with back pain and Claire in your furniture team was a pleasure to deal with, she went through the different choices with me as there was a lot and I wasn't sure which to choose. I received my chair on Tuesday and the comfort and quality is really good. I will be back to order another one for my home office.
